1.0b
2010-12-05
Renamed from animeultrastar_convert to hkt_convert.
Uses automake/autoconf makefile system.
Added commandline arguments for files (lyrics, pitches, times, output).
Uses UTF-8 (input and output).
Added support for timing file.
Uses tilde instead of hyphen for lyrics spanning multiple notes.

0.5
2010-11-27
Reads pitches and lyrics (hardcoded filenames) and outputs to standard output.
Uses new file format.
